            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/05/20230401165646761566.jpg?VersionId=48nVz6edHBCPP9VxdXKB.hKUJIdbDnd9&amp;itok=FLeDIyJi" title="中国乒乓大满贯选手张继科（右）被指利用前女友景甜私密照抵债，陷入一场舆论风暴。（互联网）" alt="中国乒乓大满贯选手张继科（右）被指利用前女友景甜私密照抵债，陷入一场舆论风暴。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/05/20230401165646761566.jpg?VersionId=48nVz6edHBCPP9VxdXKB.hKUJIdbDnd9&amp;itok=FLeDIyJi" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
